href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/partners/directory/organization/">SEI<sup>SM</sup>/CMU
Partner Directory</a>

</p>
<p>

<a href="http://www.cert.org/training/">CERT<sup>&reg;</sup> Training
and Education Courses</a>

</p>
<p>

<a href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/certification/security/csih/">CERT<sup>&reg;</sup>
Certified Computer Security Incident Handler Program</a>

</p>
<p>

<a href="http://www.cert.org/faq/cert_faq.html">The
CERT<sup>&reg;</sup> FAQ</a>

</p>

